  "detailed_description": "<strong>TOMB OF THE DEAD</strong> is a brutal arcade shooter with a classic 90s look and feel. Mow down swarms of demonic monsters and survive for as long as you can.  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163600/extras/701f582e6ac31d52b504085a73f9737f.poster.avif?t=1666158051\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163600/extras/701f582e6ac31d52b504085a73f9737f.webm?t=1666158051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163600/extras/701f582e6ac31d52b504085a73f9737f.mp4?t=1666158051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fleshy guttural sounds & evil dark ambient!<br></li><li>Pure demon slaying madness!<br></li><li>Earn points to buy better flesh weapons from a mystery carcass.<br></li><li>Use headphones! Every sound made by weapons and demons is low frequency brutality!<br></li><li>Every enemy produces ultra low guttural pulsating sounds with a rhythm. Pay close attention to the bass heavy patterns and you will survive long enough to see the worm.<br></li><li>Shoot the evil spawn towers to increase the change to get ammo.<br></li><li>Floating rib cage heads will pulverize you in seconds if not fighting hard enough.<br></li><li>Buy open doors made out of guts and flesh to expand the tight map.<br></li><li>One hardcore achievement - make it to wave 10 and get on top of the giant worm that devours everything in its path!<br></li><li>Slay massive waves of undead creatures!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163600/extras/92b705d39a01930d9568c4d983721aa8.poster.avif?t=1666158051\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163600/extras/92b705d39a01930d9568c4d983721aa8.webm?t=1666158051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163600/extras/92b705d39a01930d9568c4d983721aa8.mp4?t=1666158051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
